00:25:19.310 --> 00:25:22.760 align:middle line:10%
of the body, awaiting a moment
to resurface and continue

00:25:22.760 --> 00:25:26.330 align:middle line:10%
being processed so it can
finally be surrendered and let

00:25:26.330 --> 00:25:27.960 align:middle line:10%
go of.

00:25:27.960 --> 00:25:31.540 align:middle line:84%
Perhaps that is why these
