00:25:41.020 --> 00:25:44.310 align:middle line:10%
But once this neural
habituation has destabilized,

00:25:44.310 --> 00:25:47.100 align:middle line:10%
the natural healing
intelligence of the human being

00:25:47.100 --> 00:25:52.480 align:middle line:10%
